# Workflow Rules

Work in phases.

For every task:
1. Explain what files will change.
2. Make the smallest useful change.
3. Do not broad-refactor unrelated code.
4. Preserve working behavior.
5. Run `npm run build` when feasible.
6. Summarize changed files and remaining work.

If an instruction conflicts with existing docs, stop and ask.
If business copy requires legal/licensing claims, use cautious wording and ask.
